<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA15">
<l>pārttō retiritā neñcē paṭutuyaram</l>
<l>pērttōtap pīṭaḻivām pēccillai yārttōtan</l>
<l>tammēṉi tāṭaṭavat tāṅkiṭantu tammuṭaiya</l>
<l>cemmēṉik kaṇvaḷarvār cīr.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen understand, having encountered give [yourself], o heart,</l>
<l>once the misery that befalls [us] is destroyed there will be no talk of our perishing</l>
<l>in the greatness of [its] flood: </l>
<l>the excellence of him who slumbers with his red body, lying himself</l>
<l>while the body of the flood roars [and] strokes [his] feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
